Sentencas: Thick films of lanthanum strontium manganese oxide, La1-xSrxMnO3 (LSM), cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells, was deposited using the flame assisted vapour deposition method, a simple and cost-effective technique.
Titulo: Fabrication of cathode for solid oxide fuel cells using flame assisted vapour deposition technique

Sentencas: The surface morphology and microstructure of porous cathode films were analysed using scanning electron microscopy.
Titulo: Fabrication of cathode for solid oxide fuel cells using flame assisted vapour deposition technique

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction indicated the presence of a desirable lanthanum strontium manganese oxide phase at the deposition temperature of 710 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication of cathode for solid oxide fuel cells using flame assisted vapour deposition technique

Sentencas: The interfacial resistance between the electrode and electrolyte was measured by an AC impedance method.
Titulo: Fabrication of cathode for solid oxide fuel cells using flame assisted vapour deposition technique

Sentencas: The interfacial electrical resistance was measured to be comparable with existing literature.
Titulo: Fabrication of cathode for solid oxide fuel cells using flame assisted vapour deposition technique

Sentencas: In addition, the effect of deposition temperatures on the film's microstructure was discussed.
Titulo: Fabrication of cathode for solid oxide fuel cells using flame assisted vapour deposition technique
